data.title: William Henry Lewis and Annie Eliza Maxwell and Annie Viola Turner
data.text:
* Born in Thomas County, GA [now Grady Co.]. ** Born in Wauchula, FL.

This information was provided by Ms. Cathy Huntley, a descendent of Hassie Lewis. She found the information in the St. Andrews "Pilot" Newswaper in St. Andrews, FL.

Updates and corrections provided by Amy Lewis in July 2009.
